# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Disbursement — Cash Out ke Rekening Bank
#
# Prasyarat:
#   - Merchant harus punya saldo (lihat 04_mutation.http untuk cek balance)
#   - Merchant harus active dan CanTransact() = true
#   - Provider harus support disbursement: xendit atau doku
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl        = http://localhost:8080
@apiKey         = wpay_test_GANTI_DENGAN_API_KEY_DARI_RESPONSE
@disbursementId = GANTI_DENGAN_DISBURSEMENT_ID


### 1. Disbursement via Xendit ke BCA
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: disb-xendit-001

{
  "provider": "xendit",
  "bank_code": "BCA",
  "account_number": "1234567890",
  "account_name": "Budi Santoso",
  "amount": 500000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Pencairan saldo mingguan"
}


### 2. Disbursement via DOKU ke Mandiri
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: disb-doku-001

{
  "provider": "doku",
  "bank_code": "MANDIRI",
  "account_number": "1370012345678",
  "account_name": "Siti Rahayu",
  "amount": 250000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Refund order #98765"
}


### 3. Get detail disbursement
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements/{{disbursementId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ERROR CASES ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Provider tidak support disbursement (midtrans/ipaymu) → 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: disb-error-001

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "bank_code": "BCA",
  "account_number": "1234567890",
  "account_name": "Test",
  "amount": 100000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Test — should fail"
}


### Saldo tidak cukup → 422 Unprocessable Entity
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: disb-error-002

{
  "provider": "xendit",
  "bank_code": "BCA",
  "account_number": "1234567890",
  "account_name": "Test",
  "amount": 999999999999,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Test — saldo tidak cukup"
}
